are consistent with those of young clusters of massive stars. Point-like\nsources with non-thermal spectra are also found in the SB. These may be\nbackground objects (AGNs) or stellar remnants (neutron stars or black holes).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Oct 2003 15:33:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-13"}
