asses of neighbors that\nhave a coordination number z=12, but the evidence is insufficient for a\ndefinite unique choice. The dependence of M on the direction of H gives\nD/kB=-0.039+/-0.008K, in fair agreement with -0.031 K from earlier EPR work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Oct 2003 14:39:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-27"}
